      <h1 class='title'>Nuclear Plant Security</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 08 January 2003 vol 397 cc246-7WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_246ws' title='Col. 246WS &mdash; HC Deb 08 January 2003 vol 397 c246WS' name='column_246ws' href='#column_246ws' rel='bookmark'>246WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0397P0-06156'>
        <a name='S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_187'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-christopher-chope' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_187' title='Link to this speech by Mr Christopher Chope' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-christopher-chope" title="Mr Christopher Chope">Mr. Chope</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0397P0-06156">To ask the Secretary of State for Trade and Industry what plans he has to deploy<span class="italic">(a)</span> anti-aircraft and <span class="italic">(b)</span> ground-to-air missile batteries around nuclear power plants and nuclear fuel cycle facilities in response to the terrorist threat. [87565]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0397P0-06157'>
        <a name='S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_188'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-brian-wilson' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_188' title='Link to this speech by Mr Brian Wilson' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-brian-wilson" title="Mr Brian Wilson">Mr. Wilson</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0397P0-06157">None. Security at civil nuclear sites is ensured in a number of ways, all of which are kept under review.</p><a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_247ws' title='Col. 247WS &mdash; HC Deb 08 January 2003 vol 397 c247WS' name='column_247ws' href='#column_247ws' rel='bookmark'>247WS</a>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
